  "text": "### Scenario 2: Wrong Interest Charged  \n**Your Issue:** \"I was charged the wrong interest rate.\"  \n**What We Investigate:**\n- What rate were you supposed to receive?\n- What rate were you actually charged?\n- For how long?\n- Did this benefit or harm you?  \n**Possible Outcomes:**\n- **Our error:** Recalculate interest; refund difference + additional interest for inconvenience\n- **Policy error:** Explain policy; refund if error caused loss\n- **No error:** Explain the rate and why it's correct  \n**Typical Resolution Time:** 3–5 business days  \n---",
